<subSubSection id="C33A1BD9FFCFFF84FF1DF9033876F867" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="8B9F4852FFCFFF84FF1DF9033B65F88A" blockId="12.[151,1436,1757,1967]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<emphasis id="B9549440FFCFFF84FF1DF9033B6AF93F" bold="true" box="[198,517,1757,1783]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Distribution and habitat:</emphasis>
— 
<taxonomicName id="4C2033D1FFCFFF84FDF8F9033A76F93E" box="[547,793,1757,1782]" class="Liliopsida" family="Bromeliaceae" genus="Orthophytum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="humile">
<emphasis id="B9549440FFCFFF84FDF8F9033A76F93E" box="[547,793,1757,1782]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Orthophytum humile</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is known from Cristália and Grão Mogol counties in the state of 
<collectingRegion id="49E486B0FFCFFF84FEF1F8DC38BBF8D4" box="[298,468,1794,1820]" country="Brazil" name="Minas Gerais" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Minas Gerais</collectingRegion>
. It grows on humid or dry rocks near streams at 
<quantity id="4CD8E5B7FFCFFF84FBEDF8DC3DBEF8D4" box="[1078,1233,1794,1820]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.25" metricValueMax="10.0" metricValueMin="8.5" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="m" value="925.0" valueMax="1000.0" valueMin="850.0">850–1000 m</quantity>
elevation, often associated with termite mounts.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B9F4852FFCFFF84FF1DF8933876F867" blockId="12.[151,1436,1757,1967]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<emphasis id="B9549440FFCFFF84FF1DF8933B76F8AF" bold="true" box="[198,537,1869,1895]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">IUCN conservation status:</emphasis>
—EN B1ab (iii, iv). 
<taxonomicName id="4C2033D1FFCFFF84FCC3F8933D60F8AE" box="[792,1039,1869,1894]" class="Liliopsida" family="Bromeliaceae" genus="Orthophytum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="humile">
<emphasis id="B9549440FFCFFF84FCC3F8933D60F8AE" box="[792,1039,1869,1894]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Orthophytum humile</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
occurs in an estimated area less than 
<quantity id="4CD8E5B7FFCFFF84FF09F8AC3855F844" box="[210,314,1906,1932]" metricMagnitude="6" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="km" value="5000.0">5000 km</quantity>
<superScript id="7C55E51AFFCFFF84FEE0F8AE382CF8B6" attach="right" box="[315,323,1904,1918]" fontSize="6" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">2</superScript>
